{"tid":1034592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加藤鷹的訓練菜單　弟子：用手指挖出浴缸水","createTime":"2019-02-24T04:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T10:28:48.000Z","uid":147522,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4e6f659e8971cbef4f7188550df594ac74dbee","tid":1034592,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"出演超過1萬5千部以上的前AV男優加藤鷹，有著「金手指」、「神之手」的稱號，他的弟子吉村卓，日前上說加藤鷹要他練習用手指挖出整個浴缸的水，藉此練習手指。<br />\n<br />\n據《abematimes》報導，AbemaTV於2月15日播出的《童貞TV》(DTテレビ)節目中，邀請AV男優吉村卓大談業界秘辛，而他也是加藤鷹的弟子，說曾經住在加藤鷹家半年，然後加藤鷹就要他用手指挖出整個浴缸裡面的水當作訓練，而他也完成了2、3次，讓現場來賓各個驚嘆不已。<br />\n<br />\n而跟8000位AV女優啪啪啪過的吉村卓，也將自己理想中的最佳9人列出，分別是蕾(つぼみ)、佐倉絆、星宮一花、松本菜奈實、AIKA、三上悠亞、河合明日菜(河合あすな)、岬奈奈美(岬ななみ)、鈴村愛里(鈴村あいり)，如果要增加一名代打的話，人選是明日花綺羅(明日花キララ)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeRjPda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeRjPda.png&h=0b5daecb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pim7X6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPim7X6v.png&h=ac357367&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3ac323d8053a425a9752515b52af603599bfba4","tid":1034592,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"點挖"},{"pid":"775e3c7213ce21ea011738e331619497c8ae20b7","tid":1034592,"uid":73291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"用手指撥啲水岀黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa2c1acea84b27f498378a11db7ced6f686bdbd","tid":1034592,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"原來係兩師徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f62941659d992cc57a1d88160b390218444198","tid":1034592,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"1、4、7、8"},{"pid":"121f5dab45d32b23f94e0f8077